    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 14th level, you gain the ability to infect a humanoid's mind with the alien magic of your patron. You can use your <strong>action </strong>to touch an incapacitated humanoid. That creature is then <strong>charmed </strong>by you until a @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.ifvd6xQ8QcTIp0Rl]{Remove Curse} spell is cast on it, the charmed condition is removed from it, or you use this feature again.</p>\n<p>You can communicate telepathically with the charmed creature as long as the two of you are on the same plane of existence.</p>",
